    • generate

      public boolean generate(StructureWorldAccess world, ChunkGenerator generator, Random random, BlockPos pos)
      Generates a configured feature at the positions obtained by applying placement modifiers to the given position.

      To calculate positions, it first creates a singleton stream of the given position, then it applies placement modifiers with flatMap in order they appear in the list.
